Detailed Description

template<class MCCodeEmitterImpl>
struct llvm::RegisterMCCodeEmitter< MCCodeEmitterImpl >

RegisterMCCodeEmitter - Helper template for registering a target specific machine code emitter, for use in the target initialization function. Usage:

extern "C" void LLVMInitializeFooMCCodeEmitter() { extern Target TheFooTarget; RegisterMCCodeEmitter<FooCodeEmitter> X(TheFooTarget); }
